column2: "He still isn't anywhere to be seen..."
"You're not going to look any further than that?"
"There are a lot of enemies beyond here, we don't want to get caught up in that, do we?"
"It's okay, <%me> and I are here, so we should be able to manage."
"You're pretty much admitting that you're worthless, you realize that?"
"Why is it after us? We didn't do anything to it!"
"It's Camalots, what's he doing over there?"
"Maybe he got lost? Who knows, you need to go help him!"
"We'll take care of the enemy! While we're doing that, you need to get over there!"
"Hey! Why do I have to do something dangerous like that?!"
"Dangerous or not, in situations like this, you just need to do!"
